@startuml
actor User as U

U --> FlutterApp : Upload Image
U --> FlutterApp : Log in
U --> FlutterApp : View Potholes
U --> FlutterApp : Confirm Detection

box "Client Side (Flutter)"
    FlutterApp --> FlaskServer : POST /login
    FlutterApp --> FlaskServer : POST /upload_frame
    FlutterApp --> FlaskServer : GET /potholes
    FlutterApp -> WebSocketService : WebSocket connect for confirmation
end box

box "Server Side (Flask)"
    FlaskServer --> Database : Authenticate user
    FlaskServer --> Database : Insert uploaded image
    FlaskServer --> Database : Fetch potholes
    FlaskServer --> DetectionService : Process detection in image
    DetectionService --> FlaskServer : Pothole detected
    FlaskServer --> WebSocketService : Send confirmation request

    WebSocketService --> User : Confirm detection via WebSocket
    User --> WebSocketService : Confirmation Response (Yes/No)
    WebSocketService --> DetectionService : Forward confirmation
    DetectionService --> FlaskServer : Update image status

    FlaskServer --> Database : Update image status to PROCESSED or delete image
end box

box "Database (PostgreSQL)"
    Database --> FlaskServer : Return user data
    Database --> FlaskServer : Save uploaded image data
    Database --> FlaskServer : Update image status
end box

@enduml
